body:
@AlexeySmolenchuk 
Thank you very much for your patience in explaining and replicating the code, I noticed that your `vcpkg.json` is missing a critical part. As I said, `lcms` depends on `tools` features, so you need to modify your `vcpkg.json` file like this:
```
{
  "dependencies": [
    {
      "name": "opencolorio",
      "features": [
        "tools"
      ]
    }
  ]
```
Reference documentationï¼š https://github.com/microsoft/vcpkg-docs/blob/main/vcpkg/reference/vcpkg-json.md
